# Sprint 2 — Core Gameplay

## Zu erstellende Dateien

Alle neuen Scripts unter `Assets/_Game/Scripts/`:

| Datei | Ordner | Beschreibung |
|-------|--------|--------------|
| `ClickManager.cs` | `Gameplay/` | Manuelles Klicken → EnergySystem prüfen → EconomyManager.AddCurrency() |
| `EnergySystem.cs` | `Gameplay/` | Burnout-Mechanik: MaxEnergy, CurrentEnergy, RegenRate |
| `RaidRiskSystem.cs` | `Gameplay/` | Zoll-Risiko-Leiste + Razzia-Event bei 100% |
| `ProgressionManager.cs` | `Gameplay/` | PlayerLevel, CurrentPhase, LocationIndex, Phase-1-Unlock-Logic |
